data.description: Welcome to a charming piece of history! This 1915 home, nestled in the heart of Nampa, is a true gem featuring vintage design aesthetics from the interior doors, hardware, cabinets, craftsman window & door moldings down to the adorable retro turquoise stove. Full of potential this home is an open invitation to turn a piece of the past into your personalized masterpiece. A perfect match for both first-time homebuyers ready to take the plunge into affordable homeownership and an investor with an eye for potential and opportunity. Situated in the heart of Nampa with convenience to local amenities, parks, and schools. Complete w/ a storage shed in the back for extra storage, room for RV parking and garden boxes. New plumbing in crawlspace, water heater, kitchen sink & faucet, entry, bathroom, & laundry room flooring.
